{"tid":1814622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人純粹因為冇希望而想全香港攬炒？","createTime":"2020-01-07T03:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T00:13:32.000Z","uid":240250,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d938a312ab0db9982be69800a0a1cffc6df54d95","tid":1814622,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:43:30.000Z","msg":"你話香港剩係得五大訴求需要爭取咩？<br />\n其實我早就覺得喺香港生活(應該話係生存)係好撚冇意義。人多到仆街，樓價貴到仆街，工時長到仆街，最慘係大部分港豬都對呢套逆來順受。我屌你老母人地芬蘭準備推每週24小時工作嘅時候，我地香港人「抗爭」緊仲叫緊手停口停，返少日工都嗌晒救命，要養家呀，要供樓呀，真係難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老實講我就真係好想見到香港呢個咁嘅垃圾地方崩潰，個個冇工開，人人冇飯食就岩撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c6b1131b0439c0e3a00ce593b76e715b4baedd","tid":1814622,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:46:47.000Z","msg":"天滅港共"},{"pid":"6af78e35e923ce930d041c71207210e637b40be8","tid":1814622,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:50:40.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"6bdddcb2e2b8f7e836c6a0ef6c76fc24a7b441b7","tid":1814622,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:52:57.000Z","msg":"老老實實， agree<br />\n<br />\n醫番曬藥費<br />\n<br />\n自己諗就走好過"},{"pid":"5d598f6fa145a54d8be0163fc2380ad8e72b284b","tid":1814622,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:56:16.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#240250 - 徐永強</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>我正式宣布，大家休息至立法會選舉！！！ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>前線手足嘅血汗總算有回報，大家記住沉著冷靜，唔好再開花，免得令民意逆轉！記住血債票償呀！要喺體制內打贏佢哋！<br />\n嚟！一齊叫！光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1756452/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1756452/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>香港人終於贏左第一仗！多謝勇武手足，你地終於可以退下火線 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>首先多謝各位前線勇武手足，你地嘅血汗已經化為選票，我哋幫你報咗仇。<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fhoho.gif&h=26011529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n區選大勝，證明民意喺我哋呢邊，我哋下一步就係要建立黃色經濟圈，<br />\n等啲黃店發大嚟搞，請返留咗案底嘅手足，再下一步就係贏埋立法會選舉。<br />\n現階段抗爭運動正式轉形，最緊要唔好再搞以下幾樣野，<br />\n因為太影響民生或者畫面唔好睇，有可能會令民意反彈：<br />\n1. 堵路<br />\n2. 火魔<br />\n3. 裝修<br />\n4. 神獸<br />\n5. 黎明行動<br />\n6. 三罷<br />\n想繼續表達訴求嘅可以考慮星期日搞下遊行集會（記得要有不反），<br />\n記住唔好影響市民，唔好失民意，最好做咗都冇人知！<br />\nCome on！光復香港！時代革命！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" />[img]<a href=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gi&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=ef6f039b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi</a></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1755038/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1755038/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>運動已完，大家請接受現實 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>打左幾個月而家先返轉頭玩和理非玩感化，一定冇noise。林鄭嘅策略簡單暴力，但非常成功地將前線拉得七七八八，剩返嗰班和理非不足為患（其實對家由頭到尾都冇放和理非在眼內），就由得你喺度圍爐打飛機，打多排冇癮就自己散。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1743386/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1743386/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>請立即停止黎明行動！ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>黎明左咁多日，打工仔都適應哂，要返工嘅早兩個鐘出門口爬山都會返工，最多係遲一兩個鐘，但再搞落去只會令打工仔屌聲四起，增加民鬥民嘅情況。我呼籲大家立即停止黎明行動，準時返工返學方為上策。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1740561/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1740561/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>正式宣布黎明行動唔撚使再搞 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>好簡單既道理：一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭。<br />\n所有招數都係用一次，唔食住上星期個勢搞落去就唔使旨意再搞，你不妨睇下呢場運動有咩招數係停完之後再攞返出黎用係work既？<br />\n所以各位準時返工啦<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fsmile.gif&h=d434394b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1737015/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1737015/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/atDTbpv.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"72a34ea5c59a54ca408a39e9e6683be9e2a06c02","tid":1814622,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bdddcb2e2b8f7e836c6a0ef6c76fc24a7b441b7","tid":1814622,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:52:57.000Z","msg":"老老實實， agree<br />\n<br />\n醫番曬藥費<br />\n<br />\n自己諗就走好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:18:58.000Z","msg":"就算走唔到都唔想繼續喺個咁嘅社會生存"},{"pid":"33c004bb040f818f5a122abcffac4dd3b5ab659e","tid":1814622,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72a34ea5c59a54ca408a39e9e6683be9e2a06c02","tid":1814622,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bdddcb2e2b8f7e836c6a0ef6c76fc24a7b441b7","tid":1814622,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:52:57.000Z","msg":"老老實實， agree<br />\n<br />\n醫番曬藥費<br />\n<br />\n自己諗就走好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:18:58.000Z","msg":"就算走唔到都唔想繼續喺個咁嘅社會生存"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:28:21.000Z","msg":"諗計走囉屌你老母香港咁撚國際化 讀書唔使錢 走唔度係邊個問題"},{"pid":"541987449467bdd769f50a962e5887815b227dbc","tid":1814622,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:29:53.000Z","msg":"我係"},{"pid":"f94ed84d61712dbcf65ec6f6d042149ed50e17d9","tid":1814622,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33c004bb040f818f5a122abcffac4dd3b5ab659e","tid":1814622,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72a34ea5c59a54ca408a39e9e6683be9e2a06c02","tid":1814622,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bdddcb2e2b8f7e836c6a0ef6c76fc24a7b441b7","tid":1814622,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:52:57.000Z","msg":"老老實實， agree<br />\n<br />\n醫番曬藥費<br />\n<br />\n自己諗就走好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:18:58.000Z","msg":"就算走唔到都唔想繼續喺個咁嘅社會生存"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:28:21.000Z","msg":"諗計走囉屌你老母香港咁撚國際化 讀書唔使錢 走唔度係邊個問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:32:47.000Z","msg":"走唔走唔係重點，重點係想睇香港仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c1e85cf11f84573a2c6e231b9a8aa5a9c5341e","tid":1814622,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"541987449467bdd769f50a962e5887815b227dbc","tid":1814622,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:29:53.000Z","msg":"我係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"唔會得我地係咁諗，我相信好多人都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25cc96cdd851daa3be29be5a4af15ec0a31a815","tid":1814622,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"66c1e85cf11f84573a2c6e231b9a8aa5a9c5341e","tid":1814622,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"541987449467bdd769f50a962e5887815b227dbc","tid":1814622,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:29:53.000Z","msg":"我係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"唔會得我地係咁諗，我相信好多人都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"我最憎係香港得一套生活方式，你無得唔想做一啲嘢，因為如果你唔做，你就生存唔到，好on9，所以我先咁相信攬炒依套<br />\n唔係為香港改變，其實只係想自己第日過得好啲，只係想我條命有多小小選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d31caf7d0f816d2a960259833465644c0ddf5a5","tid":1814622,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:51:30.000Z","msg":"試下用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「冇雙普選就獨立」</span></strong>做口號<br />\n<br />\n牌面上你係爭取緊無人有異議既雙普選。實質上你提供緊清晰既路徑，解釋緊點解要獨立、以及為獨立提供正當性。<br />\n<br />\n對於和理非，一開始可以則重係「雙普選」上面。但潛移默化地灌輸佢地獨立既可行性。對於獨派，亦解決左「時機」問題；因為嚴格上口號並唔係直接提倡獨立，但同時宣傳緊獨立。"},{"pid":"df2070db6d4f921f8f02942acedecb441b0ede28","tid":1814622,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d25cc96cdd851daa3be29be5a4af15ec0a31a815","tid":1814622,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"66c1e85cf11f84573a2c6e231b9a8aa5a9c5341e","tid":1814622,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"541987449467bdd769f50a962e5887815b227dbc","tid":1814622,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:29:53.000Z","msg":"我係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"唔會得我地係咁諗，我相信好多人都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"我最憎係香港得一套生活方式，你無得唔想做一啲嘢，因為如果你唔做，你就生存唔到，好on9，所以我先咁